jbiclustge.methods.algorithms.java.bicat.auxtools

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • jbiclustge.methods.algorithms.java.bicat.auxtools.Model
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BendorReloadedModel

    public class Model
extends Object

    This is the superclass for all models. It provides fields which are indispensable for the characterization of an order-preserving submatrix.

    This class shall be extended by algorithm implementations in order to implement algorithm-specific functions on the fields.

    No field hiding is done for performance reasons. Nevertheless only subclasses of this class shall modify the fields.

    Notation:

    objectfield name
    # tissues in datasetm
    # genes in datasetn
    # tissues in submatrixs
    set of indices of tissues in submatrixT
    # planted genesk
    set of indices of genes in submatrixG
    Version:
    2004-07-22
    Author:
    Thomas Frech

        Score function according to Amir Ben-Dor.

        Warning: This function is meaningful for small parameters n and m only! For large parameters, this function evaluates to zero!

        m - # tissues in dataset
